hw6: GameCubes with Lighting and Textures

Cris Salazar
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2014



Key bindings
  ESC        Exit
  0          Reset view angle to original position
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  arrows     Change view angle
  x          Toggle axes
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  [/]        Lower/Raise light source respectively
  a/A        Toggle ambient light level
  d/D        Toggle diffuse level
  e/E        Toggle emission level
  n/N        Toggle shininess level
  p/P        Toggle GameCube motion
